736
01:09:45,399 --> 01:09:47,630
I'll always be your girl.

737
01:10:25,079 --> 01:10:30,438
And just like that,
she was gone out of my life again.

738
01:10:32,199 --> 01:10:39,150
It's one small step for man,
one giant leap for mankind.

739
01:10:43,560 --> 01:10:47,917
I thought I was going back
to Vietnam, but instead they decided

740
01:10:48,000 --> 01:10:52,073
the best way for me to fight
the communists was to play ping-pong,

741
01:10:52,159 --> 01:10:55,755
so I was in the Special Services,
travelling around the country,

742
01:10:55,840 --> 01:10:59,752
cheering up wounded veterans and
showing 'em how to play ping-pong.

743
01:10:59,840 --> 01:11:01,353
I was so good,

744
01:11:01,439 --> 01:11:04,716
