802
01:15:46,640 --> 01:15:50,427
I got to buy me one
soon as I have some money.

803
01:15:50,520 --> 01:15:51,953
I promised Bubba in Vietnam

804
01:15:52,039 --> 01:15:55,190
that as soon as the war was over,
we'd be partners.

805
01:15:55,279 --> 01:15:58,670
He'd be the captain
and I'd be his first mate.

806
01:15:58,760 --> 01:16:01,512
But now that he's dead,
I got to be the captain.

807
01:16:01,600 --> 01:16:03,430
A shrimp boat captain.

808
01:16:03,520 --> 01:16:06,556
Yes, sir. A promise is a promise,
Lieutenant Dan.

809
01:16:08,680 --> 01:16:10,556
Now hear this!

810
01:16:11,920 --> 01:16:16,198
Private Gump here is gonna be
a shrimp boat captain.

