831
01:18:41,680 --> 01:18:46,435
What's his problem? Did you lose
your packet in the war or something?

832
01:18:46,520 --> 01:18:49,273
- Is your friend stupid or something?
- What did you say?

833
01:18:49,359 --> 01:18:51,590
I said is your friend
stupid or something?

834
01:18:51,680 --> 01:18:54,432
- Don't call him stupid!
