- Yes, sir!

867
01:21:46,159 --> 01:21:51,756
As you were. I have your
discharge papers. Service is up, son.

868
01:21:53,439 --> 01:21:56,636
Does this mean
I can't play ping-pong no more?

869
01:21:56,720 --> 01:21:58,631
For the Army, it does.

870
01:22:00,520 --> 01:22:05,832
And just like that, my service
in the United States Army was over.

871
01:22:10,119 --> 01:22:12,030
So I went home.

872
01:22:32,920 --> 01:22:36,798
- I'm home, Mama.
- I know. I know.

873
01:22:38,119 --> 01:22:39,552
Louise, he's here.

874
01:22:39,640 --> 01:22:43,552
