899
01:24:15,199 --> 01:24:16,997
That's what's left after me saying,

900
01:24:17,079 --> 01:24:20,868
"When I was in China
on the All-America ping-pong team,

901
01:24:20,960 --> 01:24:22,756
"I just loved playing ping-pong

902
01:24:22,840 --> 01:24:24,909
"with my Flex-o-lite
ping-pong paddle,"

903
