01:25:26,800 --> 01:25:31,635
but there was only one
I could think of,

916
01:25:31,720 --> 01:25:35,507
the most beautiful name
in the wide world.

917
01:25:55,800 --> 01:26:01,351
I hadn't heard from Jenny in a long
